                                               DataStreamGenerator generator,
                                               int limit,

                                        throws IOException
        Open browser and shows given dataset generator's data on two dimensional plane. Label of vectors is used for ordinate representation.
        Parameters:
        name - Name of dataset for showing.
        generator - Datastream generator.
        limit - Count of points that should be taken from dataset.
        xIdx - Index of dimension for abscissa representation.
        Throws:
        IOException - IOException.

                                                 int limit,
                                                 int xIdx,
                                                 int yIdx,
                                                 boolean isLabeled)
                                          throws IOException
        Open browser and shows given dataset generator's data on two dimensional plane.
        Parameters:
        generator - Datastream generator.
        limit - Count of points that should be taken from dataset.
        xIdx - Index of dimension for abscissa representation.
        yIdx - Index of dimension for ordinate representation.
        isLabeled - if isLabeled == true then colors will be used for separate different classes on plane.
        Throws:
        IOException - IOException.
